hopobject.body: What do you study? inhouse pharmacy prescription This all leads ultimately to the direction of the share price. ASOS is a quality retailer that is growing rapidly because it offers its target audience exactly what they need and at a good price. However, the shares reflect this, and more now trading at 73 times the company’s forecast 2014 earnings. Revenue has to grow 30pc, and earnings per share (EPS) have to increase 50pc, to achieve that target.
